query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS pixel_events (
  id BIGINT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  eventId VARCHAR(64) NOT NULL UNIQUE,
  pixelUserId VARCHAR(64) NOT NULL,
  sessionId VARCHAR(64) NOT NULL,
  artistId INT,
  eventType VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  eventName VARCHAR(100),
  pageUrl TEXT,
  pageTitle VARCHAR(255),
  referrer TEXT,
  utmSource VARCHAR(100),
  utmMedium VARCHAR(100),
  utmCampaign VARCHAR(100),
  utmContent VARCHAR(100),
  utmTerm VARCHAR(100),
  deviceType VARCHAR(20),
  browser VARCHAR(50),
  os VARCHAR(50),
  country VARCHAR(2),
  region VARCHAR(100),
  city VARCHAR(100),
  ipAddress VARCHAR(45),
  userAgent TEXT,
  customData JSON,
  revenue DECIMAL(10,2),
  currency VARCHAR(3),
  productId INT,
  createdAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  INDEX pixel_user_idx (pixelUserId),
  INDEX session_idx (sessionId),
  INDEX artist_idx (artistId),
  INDEX event_type_idx (eventType),
  INDEX created_at_idx (createdAt),
  INDEX product_idx (productId)
);
